  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist, exhausted from work, checks into a secluded hotel to get some rest. It’s old but well-kept, and there are a few other guests staying there. Feeling relieved by the calm atmosphere, they quickly fall asleep to shake off their fatigue. But the moment everyone drifts off, the ordinary hotel begins to transform into a place of horror.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4356040/extras/13bc3ecf2bf706732787b4be289fbad8.poster.avif?t=1773751276\" width=454 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4356040/extras/13bc3ecf2bf706732787b4be289fbad8.webm?t=1773751276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4356040/extras/13bc3ecf2bf706732787b4be289fbad8.mp4?t=1773751276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have one goal: survive and escape the hotel that has been twisted into something else entirely. Explore its halls, unlock sealed doors, and gather clues. But be careful—relentless pursuers roam the entire hotel, searching for you, the last sacrifice they can’t afford to lose. Follow the hints left by an unknown presence, use the weapons you find, outsmart your hunters, and make it out alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4356040/extras/ebe86a5e4f03a8a4a5cb585ab986b072.poster.avif?t=1773751276\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4356040/extras/ebe86a5e4f03a8a4a5cb585ab986b072.webm?t=1773751276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4356040/extras/ebe86a5e4f03a8a4a5cb585ab986b072.mp4?t=1773751276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist, exhausted from work, checks into a secluded hotel to get some rest. It’s old but well-kept, and there are a few other guests staying there. Feeling relieved by the calm atmosphere, they quickly fall asleep to shake off their fatigue. But the moment everyone drifts off, the ordinary hotel begins to transform into a place of horror.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4356040/extras/13bc3ecf2bf706732787b4be289fbad8.poster.avif?t=1773751276\" width=454 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4356040/extras/13bc3ecf2bf706732787b4be289fbad8.webm?t=1773751276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4356040/extras/13bc3ecf2bf706732787b4be289fbad8.mp4?t=1773751276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have one goal: survive and escape the hotel that has been twisted into something else entirely. Explore its halls, unlock sealed doors, and gather clues. But be careful—relentless pursuers roam the entire hotel, searching for you, the last sacrifice they can’t afford to lose. Follow the hints left by an unknown presence, use the weapons you find, outsmart your hunters, and make it out alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4356040/extras/ebe86a5e4f03a8a4a5cb585ab986b072.poster.avif?t=1773751276\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4356040/extras/ebe86a5e4f03a8a4a5cb585ab986b072.webm?t=1773751276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4356040/extras/ebe86a5e4f03a8a4a5cb585ab986b072.mp4?t=1773751276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
